features: Perfect Compatibility - These nipple rings are specifically designed to fit seamlessly with Philips Avent Natural Original Bottles. They are identical to the original rings, ensuring a perfect match.
Secure Latch - Our rings feature a precision-engineered latch that guarantees a tight and secure fit. No more worries about leaks or spills, even if the bottle is inverted or tilted during feeding.
Convenience of Four - With a set of four replacement bottle collars, you'll always have spares at your fingertips. Whether you've lost a collar or need a quick replacement, we've got you covered.
BPA-Free for Safety - We care about your baby's health, which is why our rings are made from high-quality, BPA-free plastic. You can trust that your baby's feeding equipment is safe and toxin-free.

Easy to Use - These replacement rings are as easy to install as the originals. Simply snap them into place, and you're ready to feed your little one. *Note: Philips Avent is a registered trademark of Koninklijke Philips N.V. This product is not affiliated with or endorsed by Philips Avent.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Another good 3rd Party Replacement
reviews.reviewText: Philips Avent bottles worked really well for our babies and it is also their favorite bottle out of all the others we've tried. However, finding replacement parts on the other hand was a nightmare (Philips does sell replacement nipples, but everything else seems non existent). This nipple ring set allows us to extend the use of our bottles from our first child to the second baby, we can replace the nipples and old rings, so that he can have the same colic-free experience as his older brother. These parts also help us save money that would go towards milk, formula, and diapers.
